								</p>
							</div>
						</a>
					</li>
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell mui-media finished-order item-price mui-slider-handle">
						<div class="mui-slider-left mui-disabled">
							<a class="mui-btn mui-btn-red font12">删除</a>
						</div>
						<a href="javascript:;" class="mui-slider-handle">
							<img class="mui-media-object mui-pull-left" src="../../image/shop_05.png" alt="">
